Package: amrcartography
Title: Tools for Antimicrobial Resistance Cartography
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Andrew", "Balmer", email = "ab69@sanger.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Tools for validating MIC tables, building phenotypic distance
    structures, fitting and calibrating cartography maps, and comparing those
    maps with external distance structures. The package is designed as a
    generic MIC cartography toolkit, while retaining the S. pneumoniae
    workflow as a worked example, validation case study, and regression
    target.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/AndrewBalmer/AMRC-R-package
BugReports: https://github.com/AndrewBalmer/AMRC-R-package/issues
